OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fevening for many. Coastal low cloud
OL,7,Freturning to affect many places
OL,8,Fovernight, remaining dry with a gentle
OL,9,Fnortheasterly breeze. Feeling mild
OL,10,Fovernight but cooler along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy in the early morning
OL,13,Ffor many but soon becoming bright with
OL,14,Fhazy sunshine as the cloud retreats. A
OL,15,Fgentle northeasterly breeze persists
OL,16,Fthroughout the day, stronger along the
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
