OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and cloudy periods. The
OL,7,Fnortherly breeze introduces a fresher
OL,8,Ffeel, especially along coasts where it
OL,9,Fremains windy. Temperatures returning
OL,10,Fto around average by the weekend.
